Uttar Pradesh
Aug 30, 2014
Rape, Sexual Harassment at Work
Description:
			The principal of a madarsa here was arrested for allegedly raping his 35-year-old maid for three years.

Maulana Mursheed Ali Kadri (50) was arrested last evening after his maid lodged a complaint of sexual harassment over a period of three years, Circle Officer Ayodhya Prasad Singh said.

He said medical examination of the victim will be conducted today.

